        "body": {
            "contentType": "html",
            "content": "<html><head>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"></head><body><table class=\"block_margin\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"text-align:left; width:100%; table-layout:fixed; color:rgb(0,0,0); box-sizing:border-box; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"block_margin\" data-ogsb=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\" data-ogab=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align:left; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); padding:4px\"><table class=\"text text--padding-vertical\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"text-align:left; width:100%; table-layout:fixed; box-sizing:border-box; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" data-ogsc=\"rgb(68, 68, 68)\" data-ogsb=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\" data-ogab=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); padding:10px 40px; vertical-align:top; color:rgb(68,68,68)\"><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Hello Natalie,</span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>Client ID:</b>&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:16px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Info</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table><table class=\"block_margin\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"text-align:left; width:100%; table-layout:fixed; color:rgb(0,0,0); box-sizing:border-box; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"block_margin\" data-ogsb=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\" data-ogab=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align:left; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); padding:4px\"><table class=\"text text--padding-vertical\" id=\"table_0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"text-align:left; width:100%; table-layout:fixed; box-sizing:border-box; border-collapse:collapse; border-spacing:0px\"><tbody><tr><td class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" data-ogsc=\"rgb(68, 68, 68)\" data-ogsb=\"rgb(255, 255, 255)\" data-ogab=\"#ffffff\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; background-color:rgb(255,255,255); padding:10px 40px; vertical-align:top; color:rgb(68,68,68)\"><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">As a 2026 graduate, we want to ensure you are included in the graduating class records and yearbook! </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0); background-color:rgb(252,250,213)\">There are now <b>less than 2 weeks left</b>&nbsp;to be photographed, with the final deadline approaching on <b>Friday, March 13.</b></span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px\"><br></span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Due to the high volume of graduating seniors, appointment slots are limited and fill up quickly. We encourage you to schedule your session immediately to ensure you capture this milestone while availability remains. <b>Senior portraits are being held at the bookstore, on the lower level.</b></span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px\"><br></span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\"><b>It is <i>free</i>&nbsp;to be included in the yearbook.</b>&nbsp;Digital proofs will be provided within 5–7 business days if you wish to purchase your images for personal use or LinkedIn. When you book your appointment, you will also have the option to purchase the 2026 <i>Quad </i>Yearbook.</span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Trebuchet MS&quot;,Verdana,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px\"><br></span></p><p class=\"text_content-cell content-padding-horizontal\" style=\"text-align:left; line-height:1.2; margin:0px\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(0,0,0)\">Please visit the official scheduling portal </span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,Times,serif; font-size:17px; color:rgb(40,79,161)\"><b><u><a href=\"https://urldefense.com/v3/__https://jocrm5cab.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001zgU29xKrNzguD9Psz9Fvb72MDSH--iZGzJHZWdGOl8C1yaZk0-xfzfWHRXX08oKuvUnijhQcBzvGy5QiluWeaAV7oX-QCgav3MI7qrTQpF_WfXHKwzQ7GRbxczGEJu3eGTgigBXs7I3nJ5M6jW5BfY3oM9Xr93vY3QAWWreS9vg=&amp;c=16TTAYXxcBrk9vZxW028Ad7Q73R0ISFpfB3ux-ScJ0-BxNP7Ke0pqg==&amp;ch=yDWbk6dUA2JHnZBpGNk6UzUEuCGwOLF6BD1def3PtcegeAK4BFAD7Q==__;!!G92We9drHetJ8EofZw!a7cSWn3KPsJjmP91YN7cGfg8LHeS6LHq1ag0EuNaNMXNwRMzV19gpjaLHsAOqT76PrJY6IXL81RdPNNY2OUN$\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://urldefense.com/v3/__https://jocrm5cab.cc.rs6.net/tn.jsp?f=001zgU29xKrNzguD9Psz9Fvb72MDSH--iZGzJHZWdGOl8C1yaZk0-xfzfWHRXX08oKuvUnijhQcBzvGy5QiluWeaAV7oX-QCgav3MI7qrTQpF_WfXHKwzQ7GRbxczGEJu3eGTgigBXs7I3nJ5M6jW5BfY3oM9Xr93vY3QAWWre